Motech Industries Sigs $281 Million Contract to Buy Polysilicon From OCI

-- B y   Y u - H u a y   S u n
-- 
2011-03-17T00:59:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/motech-industries-sigs-281-million-contract-to-buy-polysilicon-from-oci.html
  Motech Industries Inc. (6244)  signed a
$281 million contract to buy polysilicon from OCI Co. through
end of 2018, Taiwan-based Motech said in a statement to the
stock exchange today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
